{"tid":1092002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地用戶數據「任攞」助獨角獸研發","createTime":"2019-04-04T13:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T00:33:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d0adf944c09fd0c9737b4e76c8991c355542d64a","tid":1092002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:40:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190404/20648510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F20648510&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=698c787e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F20648510&h=3669abda\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190404/20648510</a><br />\n<br />\n內地用戶數據「任攞」助獨角獸研發<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190404/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190404%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=abb1275a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清華大學<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】目前全球的AI發展仍以美國領先，但中國正發力追上。史丹福大學2018年10月發佈的年度全球AI報告，發佈AI論文第二多的是中國，佔比達25%，第一和第三分別是歐洲（28%）和美國（17%）。不過論AI綜合實力，報告表示還是美國最強，雖然美國的論文發佈數僅排第三，但其被引用次數卻是第一，比全球平均水準高出83%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：初創公司鬥挖角 工程師年薪70萬<br />\n<br />\n清華研究排名全球第二<br />\n<br />\n內地2016年發表的《全球人工智能發展報告（2016）》，在人工智能方面，全球排名TOP50的大學中沒有一所中國內地大學。但到2018年，據麻省理工學院發佈的最新報告，全球大學AI研究的排名，第一是卡內基梅隆大學（CMU），清華大學排名第二，康奈爾大學和史丹福大學並列第三；第五到第十名分別為：北京大學、佐治亞理工學院、華盛頓大學、加州大學伯克利分校、麻薩諸塞大學安姆斯特分校、麻省理工學院。另外，浙江大學排名第24，南京大學排名第51。<br />\n<br />\nAI研發需要依靠大量用戶數據，由於中國對用戶數據保障較薄弱，AI企業得以享受得天獨厚的環境。中國AI研發強項主要在應用層面。全球主要AI獨角獸（即未上市公司）中，中國的字節跳動、商湯科技均排市值榜前列。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n財經專題：華企押巨注抗美 AI晶片反擊戰<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n初創公司鬥挖角 工程師年薪70萬<br />\n<br />\n初創公司鬥挖角 工程師年薪70萬<br />\n藉人工智能佈「天網」監控民眾<br />\n財經專題：華企押巨注抗美AI晶片反擊戰"},{"pid":"8cbd5224583fef02632e5b776e2feadb2caced5c","tid":1092002,"uid":161988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"仲以為係可以爆甲個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62d48a66c4cf1526274244eb0a11aa7496e9f56","tid":1092002,"uid":121771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"仲以為講緊高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a402b678c3936609ce785fb9df3ac8ce4b8fa97","tid":1092002,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cbd5224583fef02632e5b776e2feadb2caced5c","tid":1092002,"uid":161988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"仲以為係可以爆甲個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"爸娜滋"},{"pid":"b2062cc4cd28903af6a1d6d56a748d2dd69ce378","tid":1092002,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"以前就話大陸嗰兩間u冇排名係政治因素<br />\n依家又浸佢玩係咩原因？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf6c2ac4393cc0e8bc02c75a09c8c9d3a1255a4","tid":1092002,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62d48a66c4cf1526274244eb0a11aa7496e9f56","tid":1092002,"uid":121771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"仲以為講緊高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"我對內容好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}